WEBVTT

00:07.441 --> 00:09.910
NOW, MAY I PRESENT
TO Y'ALL,

00:09.977 --> 00:12.246
EVERY WRESTLING FAN'S
FANTASY:

00:12.313 --> 00:15.649
THE BOSEPHEUS
JUMBO WRESTLING BOWL!

00:15.716 --> 00:16.917
[ALL GASPING]

00:16.984 --> 00:19.587
THE LARGEST WRESTLING-ONLY
FACILITY IN THE WORLD,

00:19.653 --> 00:23.791
BUILT BY YOURS TRULY,
BRODERICK BOSEPHEUS!

00:23.857 --> 00:25.259
WHO IS ME.

00:25.326 --> 00:27.095
AN UNDERWATER CAGE,

00:27.161 --> 00:29.397
A HIGH-TECH
HYDRAULIC PLATFORM,

00:29.463 --> 00:31.932
GRAVITY-DEFYING ZIP-LINES.

00:31.999 --> 00:33.334
IT'S ALL HERE!

00:33.401 --> 00:35.903
NOW, IF Y'ALL
WILL EXCUSE ME,

00:35.969 --> 00:37.805
I NEED TO PREPARE
FOR THE EVENT.

00:37.871 --> 00:39.340
BUT DON'T Y'ALL WORRY.

00:39.407 --> 00:41.309
HERE'S A LITTLE
DEMONSTRATION

00:41.375 --> 00:43.811
I KNOW Y'ALL GONNA ENJOY.

00:50.084 --> 00:52.453
RARR! RARRRRR!

00:53.521 --> 00:54.522
AAAH!

00:54.588 --> 00:55.623
[GASPING]

00:55.689 --> 00:57.191
ARRRR!

00:59.760 --> 01:01.729
AAAAAAH!

01:01.795 --> 01:03.597
ARR!
HA HA HA HA HA!

01:03.664 --> 01:07.268
ARR! ARR! ARR!
ARR! ARR! ARR! ARR!

01:09.903 --> 01:11.004
* WHAT'S NEW, SCOOBY-DOO? *

01:11.071 --> 01:12.473
* WE'RE COMING AFTER YOU *

01:12.540 --> 01:15.176
* WE'RE GONNA SOLVE
THAT MYSTERY *

01:15.243 --> 01:16.644
* I SEE YOU, SCOOBY-DOO *

01:16.710 --> 01:18.279
* THE TRAIL
LEADS BACK TO YOU *

01:18.346 --> 01:21.048
* WHAT'S NEW, SCOOBY-DOO? *

01:21.115 --> 01:22.583
* WHAT'S NEW, SCOOBY-DOO? *

01:22.650 --> 01:24.084
* WE'RE GONNA FOLLOW YOU *

01:24.152 --> 01:27.288
* YOU'RE GONNA SOLVE
THAT MYSTERY *

01:27.355 --> 01:28.856
* WE SEE YOU, SCOOBY-DOO *

01:28.922 --> 01:30.158
* WE'RE COMING AFTER YOU *

01:30.224 --> 01:33.527
* WHAT'S NEW, SCOOBY-DOO? *

01:34.928 --> 01:36.297
* DON'T LOOK BACK *

01:36.364 --> 01:39.400
* YOU MAY FIND
ANOTHER CLUE *

01:40.768 --> 01:45.206
* SCOOBY SNAX WILL BE
WAITING HERE FOR YOU *

01:45.273 --> 01:46.440
* WHAT'S NEW, SCOOBY-DOO? *

01:46.507 --> 01:47.808
* WE'RE COMING AFTER YOU *

01:47.875 --> 01:50.911
* WE'RE GONNA SOLVE
THAT MYSTERY *

01:50.978 --> 01:52.313
* I SEE YOU, SCOOBY-DOO *

01:52.380 --> 01:53.547
* THE TRAIL
